It was submitted that AOR are given pre-eminence position as they:

 (i) Undertake an examination administered by the Supreme Court;
 (ii) Are the only advocates authorised to act on behalf of a client in the Supreme Court;
 (iii) Adhere to strict stipulations regarding office location, maintenance of accounts and filing of returns, unlike any other class of advocates.

